title: Ben Webster - 1970 - Stormy Weather (2012 vinyl 24 96) FLAC
description:
Ben Webster - 1970 - Stormy Weather (2012)
45 RPM vinyl, 24 bits, 96 KHz

Recorded around a month after the veteran tenor Ben Webster moved to Europe, this high-quality set with pianist Kenny Drew, bassist Niels Pederson, and drummer Alex Riel features Webster stretching out on the traditional "Londonderry Air," two originals, and seven familiar but fresh standards. Webster, although neglected in the U.S., was still in peak form in the mid-'60s, as this and his other Black Lion sets covering the period show. (AllMusic)
